Click to launch the simulation:
<p><a href="bernoulli.jnlp"><img alt="Screenshot" src="bernoulli.gif"
 style="border: 2px solid ;"></a></p>
Directions (this simulation is not user-friendly):<br>
<ul>
  <li>Tabs at the top choose between modules</li>
  <li>Clicking on the faucet opens it.</li>
  <li>Dragging a water tower changes the height</li>
  <li>You can manually drag the pump piston.</li>
  <li>You can turn on the pump with it's button.</li>
  <li>You can change the shape of the pipe by dragging its control
points.<br>
  </li>
</ul>
